>> Servings: 12 pieces
>> Difficulty: Medium

Preheat the oven to 200 degrees. 

Mix the @oats{200%g}, @almond flour{100%g}, @baking powder{2%tbsp} and @salt{a pinch of} in a #bowl{}. Add the mashed @bananas{2}, @oat milk{250%ml} and melted @ghee{80%g}. Finally add the frozen/fresh @raspberries{150%g}.

Pour the mixture into a #silicone muffin tray{}.

Bake for about ~{25 minutes}.
